==Basque==

===Pronunciation===
* /gausa/

===Noun===
'''gauza'''
# that which is considered to exist as a separate entity or concept; [[thing]].
# Word that can be used to refer to any physical or psychical entity.

===Adjective===
'''gauza'''
# Having sufficient power, strength, force, skill, means, or [[resources]] of any kind to accomplish the object; possessed of [[qualifications]] rendering [[competent]] for some end; [[competent]]; [[qualified]]; capable;  [[able]], [[capable]], [[apt]].
#:'''Examples'''
#:*''zerbait egiteko gauza izan - to be able to do something''.
#:*''ez naiz egiteko gauza izan - I'm not been able to do it''.

